           MOVE XDJL4125-O-LNBZ-I-HGST-LIMT
             TO YPJL4125-LNBZ-I-HGST-LIMT
      *   그룹명
           MOVE XDJL4125-O-AFFLT-C-GROUP-NAME
             TO YPJL4125-AFFLT-C-GROUP-NAME
      *   유효기일
           MOVE XDJL4125-O-MGT-LIMT-VALD-YMD
             TO YPJL4125-MGT-LIMT-VALD-YMD
      *   포괄신용공여관리한도
           MOVE XDJL4125-O-MGT-CLAM
             TO YPJL4125-MGT-CLAM
      *   그룹신용등급
           MOVE XDJL4125-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD
             TO YPJL4125-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD
      *   업종명
           MOVE XDJL4125-O-STND-IDSTRY-CD-NAME
             TO YPJL4125-STND-IDSTRY-CD-NAME
      * 2011.06.03최종적용포괄한도　추가
           MOVE XDJL4125-O-LAST-INLS-LIMT
             TO YPJL4125-LAST-INLS-LIMT
      *   기업신용등급
           MOVE XDJL4125-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD1
             TO YPJL4125-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD1

220324*   부실회계기업등급
           PERFORM  S6100-IJL4009-CALL-RTN
              THRU  S6100-IJL4009-CALL-EXT

      *   기사용액
           MOVE XDJL4125-O-INLS-GRCR-LIMT-AUC
             TO YPJL4125-INLS-GRCR-LIMT-AUC
      *   한도여유액
           MOVE XDJL4125-O-LIMT-SEXTR-AMT
             TO YPJL4125-LIMT-SEXTR-AMT

      *@4.2 출력라인수 조립
           MOVE XDJL4125-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
             TO YPJL4125-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

      *@4.3 그리드1 조립
      *@실행조건:WK-I > YPJL4125-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
      *@처리내용:그리드1 조립
           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
                   UNTIL   WK-I > YPJL4125-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

                   MOVE XDJL4125-O-GRID1(WK-I)
                     TO YPJL4125-GRID1(WK-I)
           END-PERFORM

220324*   별도전결권적용금액
           MOVE XDJL4125-O-SEPA-DAR-APLY-AMT
             TO YPJL4125-SEPA-DAR-APLY-AMT
           .

       S6000-OUTPUT-EXT.
           EXIT.

