       S6100-IJL4009-CALL-RTN.

           INITIALIZE                  XIJL4009-IN

      *@1  입력파라미터 조립
      *    KB-PIN
           MOVE  YNJL4125-KB-PIN
             TO  XIJL4009-I-KB-PIN

      *@1  IC부실회계기업 등급조회 프로그램 호출
           #DYCALL  IJL4009  YCCOMMON-CA  XIJL4009-CA

           IF  COND-XIJL4009-OK
      *       부실회계기업등급
               MOVE XIJL4009-O-INSL-A-GRD-DSTCD
                 TO YPJL4125-INSL-ACCTG-CORP-GRD
           ELSE
      *       부실회계기업등급
               MOVE '0'
                 TO YPJL4125-INSL-ACCTG-CORP-GRD
           END-IF
           .

       S6100-IJL4009-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.

